<a name = "ComplexFuncions"><b> Complex Functions </b></a>
<p>
	Examples: $e^{i\theta}z, e^z,  \frac{1}{z}.$
	<ul>
		<li>
			Exponential function:
			\[
				e^z = e^{x + iy} = e^x(\cos y + i\sin y).
			\]
		</li>
		<li>
			Logarithmic function:
			\[
				\log(z) = \ln |z| + i\arg(z). 
			\]
		</li>
		<li>
			Principal-value logarithmic function:
			\[
				\text{Log}(z) = \ln |z| + i\text{Arg}(z), 
			\]
			where $\text{Arg}(z)$ is in the range $(-\pi,\pi].$
		</li>
	</ul>
</p>